00:48:51.451 --> 00:48:53.647
You remind me of him more and more every day.

00:48:55.053 --> 00:48:56.975
But you will always be our son.

00:49:00.431 --> 00:49:01.320
Thank you, father.

00:49:26.041 --> 00:49:27.384
Sachiko, do you see it?

00:49:27.400 --> 00:49:28.334
Is there any answer?

00:49:28.359 --> 00:49:29.151
Not yet.

00:49:40.888 --> 00:49:42.980
