00:50:48.616 --> 00:50:49.450
It's OK.

00:50:49.475 --> 00:50:50.848
I know you have to get to school.

00:50:52.203 --> 00:50:53.355
I'm going to miss you.

00:50:54.414 --> 00:50:55.745
I'll drop by now and then.

00:50:56.124 --> 00:50:57.081
Now, go.

00:50:57.117 --> 00:50:58.203
Before I start crying.

00:50:59.127 --> 00:50:59.733
Mm-hm.

00:51:02.470 --> 00:51:04.647
I hope everything works out with you and Shun.

00:51:04.851 --> 00:51:05.343
Huh?

00:51:10.210 --> 00:51:11.155
Take care, Miki.

